Hi Steve.  If I stop the playback just a little shorter, I hear, &quot;I hope you hear&quot; perfectly.  
Otherwise, it comes out, &quot;I hope you him.&quot;  I&#39;ve noticed this a lot the last few days, that 
some areas sort of blend and I have to cut a segment off where it visually looks as though 
it would be in the middle of a word, but it isn&#39;t (if that makes sense).  

If you get a chance, see if you can get the name of who is speaking.  I was very surprised 
to learn &quot;Arthur&quot; is the tech for me with EVPM, and one of my regular techs (David) even 
confirmed this information via a manual radio sweep.  Fun stuff!!

Margaret

